Imzalen d yiwet n taddart di tama n [[Iflisen Umellil|Yeflisen Umellil]]. 

==Azar n Wawal==

Anamek n wawal-aki, yekka-d seg Amzak (asget ines d-IMZALEN), seg zik, lɛarc-aki id yuskan di tama n yeflisen uɣen cciɛa imi tugett gar-asen d Iḥeddaden (forgeron). Seg ayaki id yekka AMZAL: Win iseqdacen uzzal. Ula d tamacahutt-nni n uḥeddad uqalus, t beggned anect-a. AQALUS di zzman tuɣ-itt t-d-tekka ar Yeflisen. 

